Fourth‐order Mo/ller–Plessett perturbation theory in the local correlation treatment. I. Method
J. Chem. Phys. 86 , 914 (1987); https://doi.org/10.1063/1.452293
Svein Saebo/
Department of Chemistry, Mississippi State University, Mississippi State, Mississippi 39762
Peter Pulay
Department of Chemistry, University of Arkansas, Fayetteville, Arkansas 72701
more...

